column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, (#*s.z/#) as dist,  err_u, err_g, err_r, err_i, err_z, extinction_u, extinction_g, extinction_r, extinction_i, extinction_z FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class = galaxy&&&
